17-01-28T22:35:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我媽咪07走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今年第十年<br />\n癌症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係肺癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef1bd605573dd15d9c3fce76e2572b7485f634a","tid":98984,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T22:42:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我媽咪07走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今年第十年<br />\n癌症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我一個好親嘅人都係07年走<br />\n不過係自行了斷<br />\n啱啱發夢見到佢<br />\n醒左之後喊左一場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n十年喇，你過得幾好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea30514b3f3a6de84379fa9da2df27184b0faf0","tid":98984,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T22:43:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我媽咪07走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今年第十年<br />\n癌症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同我爸爸同年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都係癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb98cbd4b0656880542b4db8397247f6eace93d","tid":98984,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T22:46:37.000Z","msg":"唉，cancer真係恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f01126ffc3330b1c4e4684743823f5de879b6b4","tid":98984,"uid":369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T22:51:06.000Z","msg":"想喊就喊<br />\n阿媽13年過新年時候走<br />\n嗰陣覺得個世界真係灰色<br />\n每日訓醒都希望自己係發緊夢"},{"pid":"c43e707f64932240623e07bcce0cfcbfddfbf279","tid":98984,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T22:51:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唉，cancer真係恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好驚有一日到自己"},{"pid":"e58b90750c23007c6473a3a905df0780dab379aa","tid":98984,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T22:51:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想喊就喊<br />\n阿媽13年過新年時候走<br />\n嗰陣覺得個世界真係灰色<br />\n每日訓醒都希望自己係發緊夢</blockquote><br />\n就係呢種感覺<br />\n真係好想只係一場夢"},{"pid":"dd8f31fbcb0411957bb3e05f5eae78d901e0c3b1","tid":98984,"uid":80310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T22:53:46.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲撐住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n媽媽成日同我講，第時佢地過左身<br />\n就得返啊妹係我最親既人<br />\n每次諗起都眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利: 同妹關係良好"},{"pid":"8950c9671e8c5fc1deb422ba6963fdf551de5b94","tid":98984,"uid":369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T22:54:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想喊就喊<br />\n阿媽13年過新年時候走<br />\n嗰陣覺得個世界真係灰色<br />\n每日訓醒都希望自己係發緊夢</blockquote><br />\n就係呢種感覺<br />\n真係好想只係一場夢</blockquote><br />\n然後訓醒左知道係現實<br />\n每日都...心如刀割<br />\n都唔記得嗰陣點過"},{"pid":"2cf7808bc930c7587df32dbe628637786b84904f","tid":98984,"uid":36097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T22:55:29.000Z","msg":"老豆上年今日（初二晚）意外去左"},{"pid":"260928ebbc1309a824764182a366c4b304576bb1","tid":98984,"uid":1274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T22:57:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老豆上年今日（初二晚）意外去左</blockquote><br />\n有無聽過意外去世喺幸福！"},{"pid":"14d76ed3aff95941aacc2b76e0ae7cbc17ff9546","tid":98984,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T22:59:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想喊就喊<br />\n阿媽13年過新年時候走<br />\n嗰陣覺得個世界真係灰色<br />\n每日訓醒都希望自己係發緊夢</blockquote><br />\n就係呢種感覺<br />\n真係好想只係一場夢</blockquote><br />\n然後訓醒左知道係現實<br />\n每日都...心如刀割<br />\n都唔記得嗰陣點過</blockquote><br />\n我都有同一個問題<br />\n答案就係好難捱咁捱過<br />\n巴打其實你好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6545eed5460bed3aca57af3e04760e8afbc232ea","tid":98984,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T22:59:42.000Z","msg":"從來未有過<br />\n唔知道有媽媽係咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f931102ca84aaa547ff045861c431d05d705f1e8","tid":98984,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T23:00:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老豆上年今日（初二晚）意外去左</blockquote><br />\n阿媽點?"},{"pid":"c1bcc665001fc98387377d864ccddd8c5775fe56","tid":98984,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T23:01:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老豆上年今日（初二晚）意外去左</blockquote><br />\n有無聽過意外去世喺幸福！</blockquote><br />\n我真係聽過醫院有人用呢句安慰人<br />\n但當然係反效果"},{"pid":"00a2edb2ebf0bb94f319aba5f83a09b366e1593a","tid":98984,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T23:02:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>從來未有過<br />\n唔知道有媽媽係咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第時你生細路，記得比一個佢<br />\n到時可能會感受到少少"},{"pid":"f3ff9d0e3fdb78bdb501d2f7f71a06dbc2056a5f","tid":98984,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T23:02:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>老豆上年今日（初二晚）意外去左</blockquote><br />\n有無聽過意外去世喺幸福！</blockquote><br />\n我真係聽過醫院有人用呢句安慰人<br />\n但當然係反效果</blockquote><br />\n痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac7d71243ade82bf62bfa534cab51dd9c4099b4","tid":98984,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T23:03:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>老豆上年今日（初二晚）意外去左</blockquote><br />\n有無聽過意外去世喺幸福！</blockquote><br />\n我真係聽過醫院有人用呢句安慰人<br />\n但當然係反效果</blockquote><br />\n痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBTW, 巴打又會咁早?"},{"pid":"e98b2337a7cdfea7c22c6a513f437d7a6219fc94","tid":98984,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T23:03:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>從來未有過<br />\n唔知道有媽媽係咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n另類慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有媽的孩子像個寶"},{"pid":"408ab79c54297547e54b8c157e7df0eb279815dc","tid":98984,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T23:03:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>從來未有過<br />\n唔知道有媽媽係咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第時你生細路，記得比一個佢<br />\n到時可能會感受到少少</blockquote><br />\n又或者係因為本身家庭唔完整<br />\n更加會確定除非俾到一個正常既環境子女<br />\n否則唔會生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d08ac796d0a0465d093dd02c451a6f75f79b8c8","tid":98984,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T23:03:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我真係聽過醫院有人用呢句安慰人<br />\n但當然係反效果</blockquote><br />\n痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBTW, 巴打又會咁早?</blockquote><br />\n？"},{"pid":"463f499ecfd6386e2b19d9eff24028d00e7f4daf","tid":98984,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T23:04:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>從來未有過<br />\n唔知道有媽媽係咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n另類慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有媽的孩子像個寶</blockquote><br />\n唔知係好事定壞事<br />\n從來都無得到過，就唔會失去<br />\n取而代之既係細細個開始已經所有野都自己搞掂<br />\n會比一般同年紀既人成熟"},{"pid":"7e1f176537838d8e494d803b92fd621aac9ea337","tid":98984,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T23:05:24.000Z","msg":"一歲未夠，佢就因病過咗身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3fafab2c6b2f682c05bab08740b1fac6518c50e","tid":98984,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T23:07:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n唔知係好事定壞事<br />\n從來都無得到過，就唔會失去<br />\n取而代之既係細細個開始已經所有野都自己搞掂<br />\n會比一般同年紀既人成熟</blockquote><br />\n同我諗法一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我唔會因為缺母愛而唔開心<br />\n相反地，經常被小學同學和家長歧視、班主任當正我有心理病<br />\n另加親戚睇唔起我背後鬧我冇老母<br />\n呢啲先至係真正令我唔開心嘅事"},{"pid":"f05418b46c51bf84491761abe488bda3afa38ac4","tid":98984,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T23:08:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我真係聽過醫院有人用呢句安慰人<br />\n但當然係反效果</blockquote><br />\n痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBTW, 巴打又會咁早?</blockquote><br />\n？</blockquote><br />\nsorry我傻左唔使理我個問題<br />\n<br />\n辦啲手續有人幫手嗎？"},{"pid":"54c3132ddc905d8ce8f12349acbee41ac7616879","tid":98984,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T23:09:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>從來未有過<br />\n唔知道有媽媽係咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第時你生細路，記得比一個佢<br />\n到時可能會感受到少少</blockquote><br />\n又或者係因為本身家庭唔完整<br />\n更加會確定除非俾到一個正常既環境子女<br />\n否則唔會生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個諗法都係你經驗之談<br />\n其實好正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff827a3bb9c5666790cb3a9ec966e84c5b2f66f","tid":98984,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T23:10:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n唔知係好事定壞事<br />\n從來都無得到過，就唔會失去<br />\n取而代之既係細細個開始已經所有野都自己搞掂<br />\n會比一般同年紀既人成熟</blockquote><br />\n同我諗法一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我唔會因為缺母愛而唔開心<br />\n相反地，經常被小學同學和家長歧視、班主任當正我有心理病<br />\n另加親戚睇唔起我背後鬧我冇老母<br />\n呢啲先至係真正令我唔開心嘅事</blockquote><br />\n人係鍾諗拎自己擁有嘅野去打J，同時拎黎區分自己同其他人"},{"pid":"8c6fb0ff97fb4f3e202c270748a34f6b87607570","tid":98984,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T23:10:37.000Z","msg":"樓主，起碼你同你媽相見過係一種緣份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔係恨有母愛<br />\n但我都想知我媽大概係個點嘅人<br />\n<br />\n以前佢有寫落好多信比我<br />\n我親戚扔曬，話唔想留「死人嘢」係屋度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我媽係個點嘅人，我真係唔知道"},{"pid":"a752aed9cdf89fdc0e016c5265244971de4f1586","tid":98984,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T23:10:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\nBTW, 巴打又會咁早?</blockquote><br />\n？</blockquote><br />\nsorry我傻左唔使理我個問題<br />\n<br />\n辦啲手續有人幫手嗎？</blockquote><br />\n醫生都未黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"971afeb0e2fdbd1ff37c05555213423f8e601aaf","tid":98984,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T23:11:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人係鍾諗拎自己擁有嘅野去打J，同時拎黎區分自己同其他人</blockquote><br />\n啲人拎有冇老母去睇唔起人<br />\n真係賤過乜咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"991ae0f08cec05fa0460dab9e1cb54fde2939a8f","tid":98984,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T23:15:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人係鍾諗拎自己擁有嘅野去打J，同時拎黎區分自己同其他人</blockquote><br />\n啲人拎有冇老母去睇唔起人<br />\n真係賤過乜咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n或者過份同情<br />\n以為你地過得好慘"},{"pid":"fe5d99a0c30e5c3708f632bf501a4ee1479956bf","tid":98984,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T23:17:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\nBTW, 巴打又會咁早?</blockquote><br />\n？</blockquote><br />\nsorry我傻左唔使理我個問題<br />\n<br />\n辦啲手續有人幫手嗎？</blockquote><br />\n醫生都未黎<img src=\"/assets/faces