re":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T03:19:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係呢度既巴絲打個個都好堅強<br />\n樓主節哀，的確會好難受<br />\n但時間會沖淡你既傷心<br />\n<br />\n我而家連阿媽把聲都唔記得<br />\n好後悔無錄落黎</blockquote><br />\n有錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nwhatsapp有佢把聲 到而家都唔敢聽"},{"pid":"60a675a26a063953ec9b0edb7e6dfdce5c46371e","tid":98984,"uid":49626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T03:20:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n頂住呀巴打<br />\n7年前走左果時會考都冇心機考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nCancer<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又係cancer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n節哀順變 <br />\n最後我見佢走左反而鬆一口氣 睇住佢日日咁辛苦仲傷心"},{"pid":"d34c91135ca59d02c92be8db346c9f6ffe7450b5","tid":98984,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T03:44:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係呢度既巴絲打個個都好堅強<br />\n樓主節哀，的確會好難受<br />\n但時間會沖淡你既傷心<br />\n<br />\n我而家連阿媽把聲都唔記得<br />\n好後悔無錄落黎</blockquote><br />\n有錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nwhatsapp有佢把聲 到而家都唔敢聽</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f2cb144b4a3b9e97fe2aacf0d47798fe12ed71","tid":98984,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T03:50:38.000Z","msg":"爸爸唔係到<br />\n3年前返返下工就去左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇任何預兆"},{"pid":"f619d466d83cb0f08b639e10f97e604070016bff","tid":98984,"uid":42569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T03:57:32.000Z","msg":"加油巴打"},{"pid":"99c3e642c3372beba5218a0be7cd66de78c8bfe2","tid":98984,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:05:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n頂住呀巴打<br />\n7年前走左果時會考都冇心機考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nCancer<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又係cancer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n節哀順變 <br />\n最後我見佢走左反而鬆一口氣 睇住佢日日咁辛苦仲傷心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲記得媽咪走嗰日我喺學校，食緊早餐嗰陣校務處突然嗌咪叫我個名，其實我都心知係咩事，去到校務處校工話舅父嚟咗要接我去醫院。見到舅父嗰陣佢話媽咪已經走咗喇，當時我個心好平靜，因為媽咪已經病咗好多年，佢終於唔駛再受苦了。去完醫院之後本身阿爸叫我返屋企抖吓，但我堅持要返學，當我返到班房班主任見到我時佢露出一臉驚慌嘅表情，然後夜晚佢打比舅父話佢好擔心我，因為我個人太平靜，一滴眼淚都無流過仲好正常咁返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de84433de343f8847d1573d1df849e0631634b0c","tid":98984,"uid":38981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:16:09.000Z","msg":"爸媽都已經走左。<br />\n<br />\n本人今年只係30"},{"pid":"cf8b3e2545b7c9d2e0ef785db1de4e61ff33b4c2","tid":98984,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T05:23:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爸媽都已經走左。<br />\n<br />\n本人今年只係30</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f00fe49a6388d87d11a94395db92077c1f8f79","tid":98984,"uid":6903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T05:38:48.000Z","msg":"得返啊媽一個<br />\n細細個諗過如果佢走左會係點<br />\n每次都會諗到眼濕濕<br />\n但過後又會冇左件事<br />\n可能重會做啲好對唔住佢嘅事<br />\n加上又唔會表達自己有幾愛佢<br />\n好怕真係會子欲養而親不在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf9b5f4e5673e8e4de736e130623ffc28880438","tid":98984,"uid":80364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T05:39:32.000Z","msg":"一樣<br />\n細個成日打我，屌我，劈me<br />\n佢有少少精神病<br />\n到大個選擇自己離開<br />\n搶左層樓<br />\n令到間樓變成兇宅，生活好難過<br />\n<br />\n由細到大冇同親人點講野，好冇attachment<br />\n有焦慮症<br />\n有少少憎佢<br />\n但又會掛住<br />\n<br />\n唔敢對任何人有感情<br />\n要面其實怕鐘意人會受傷<br />\n<br />\n但就要番一份成日對人要講野既工<br />\n突破唔到陰影，同人講野會心悸好撚毒<br />\n點搞？！"},{"pid":"b58583c90682962bc4d73c9a0f3f5cdccd0eea0e","tid":98984,"uid":369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T05:49:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>爸媽都已經走左。<br />\n<br />\n本人今年只係30</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁呢幾年你點呀<br />\n支持住"},{"pid":"98331c05e4298928bca2ca88da322d7ab265dd5e","tid":98984,"uid":1876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T05:57:30.000Z","msg":"我隻貓啱啱都走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f428a35510928c193519014cd4710757676a3101","tid":98984,"uid":17618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T05:59:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爸媽都已經走左。<br />\n<br />\n本人今年只係30</blockquote><br />\n同你一樣<br />\n大你一啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df95d9603f19bd9df9d31517126564d23289be2","tid":98984,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T08:25:33.000Z","msg":"點先可以見返佢，我好心痛<br />\n<br />\n佢最後有清醒意識同我講既野就係<br />\n<br />\n「對唔住啊，以前我團年飯都會煮好多野食」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d82428191bf10ab6f7cfd5e97d43135be16e34","tid":98984,"uid":23218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:00:48.000Z","msg":"爸爸幾年前唔係到 而家一諗佢就喊"},{"pid":"cb39b1a57b8945e8b88df9be0417a31c25bbdbe7","tid":98984,"uid":13747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:02:10.000Z","msg":"我媽媽上年新年前無啦啦走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cba5e0b05774ed22fea6ef0793fb3c8c9b32cb5","tid":98984,"uid":58066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:08:48.000Z","msg":"媽媽10年走左 同年養左13年貓仔都走埋<br />\n上年比老豆趕走埋 睇盡晒所謂既屋企人<br />\n同自己講過一定要活得比佢地好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：今年29"},{"pid":"a2f010f57b2a4f4e94d331442afced81afabde2d","tid":98984,"uid":57460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:12:27.000Z","msg":"爸爸十幾年前去左，嗰時我初中。<br />\n要同自己講屋企得返自己一個係男性，<br />\n所以要堅強。<br />\n<br />\n巴打你都要撐住！"},{"pid":"fe362862a48f4a3860ea52023849639c43bf9f0a","tid":98984,"uid":38981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:24:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>爸媽都已經走左。<br />\n<br />\n本人今年只係30</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁呢幾年你點呀<br />\n支持住</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n媽係我3歲已經走左，老豆上年走。<br />\n<br />\n有阿哥，一齊生活，日子都係咁過。"},{"pid":"e573a6daec9f80c9f9a46041e04c0118cbd1f302","tid":98984,"uid":369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:55:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點先可以見返佢，我好心痛<br />\n<br />\n佢最後有清醒意識同我講既野就係<br />\n<br />\n「對唔住啊，以前我團年飯都會煮好多野食」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我完全明<br />\n我個case係...阿媽叫我地聽朝十二點叫佢再黎探佢<br />\n凌晨4點就走左<br />\n個心覺得好撚悔恨<br />\n成件事好無力<br />\n<br />\n你媽媽在天之靈會睇住你<br />\n而家我三五七時都會搵我阿媽黎講笑<br />\n都睇開左<br />\n但有時一諗起都會忍唔住"},{"pid":"0abb5d7f3ae52ef647b5bb8a79110e79d4b4c59b","tid":98984,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T10:04:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37ec19616ffd64024135f422f7d4ec96b268e862","tid":98984,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T10:49:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以後要堅強<br />\n時間會一日一日咁提升你嘅接受能力<br />\n初頭真係會好難過<br />\n今朝諗起都好唔開心，雖然已經過左十年<br />\n所以要好好咁紀念佢<br />\n做好自己，唔好令媽媽生前對你嘅期望白廢<br />\n撐住呀!"}]}